Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two famous archaeologists have discovered a series of underground passageways leading to an ancient civilization. The duo packed their bags full of necessary supplies, turned on their headlights, and crawled into the hole that led to an underground structure.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The duo tie a rope and climb down.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Before proceeding, Sam rubs their hand along the ground to check for traps.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Sam triggers a pressure plate. A hidden passage leading forward opens up in front of him.
Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Sam finds no traps so he decides it is safe to continue forward.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Sam touches the ground triggering a pressure plate. This releases a boulder which falls grazing his shoulder dealing damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The duo continues into a dark and narrow underground cave.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Jack turns on their flashlight to illuminate the way forward.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Jack’s light illuminates a gemstone vein along the cavern wall. He chips off and adds a few gemstones to their pack.
Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Jack uses the light to make it easier for him to continue forward with no issues.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The light disturbs a flock of bats, which fly past Jack causing him to drop several rations from their pack.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Jack tries to shoo them away.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Jack causes the salamander to run back to their hole leaving him alone.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The salamander’s poisonous skin brushes against Jack and runs away. He is left with an irritated rash dealing damage.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Sam makes it over and he continues on.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Sam slips and falls into the puddle. He gets bit by numerous leeches dealing damage.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Jack steps on the false floor revealing its secrets.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Jack reveals a deep crater in the floor. He covers the hole with the carpet again.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Jack steps into a hidden tar trap. He feels increasingly exhausted from having to remove her foot from the trap.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: A snake leaps out biting Sam’s arm. He takes damage and uses a bandage to their arm.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Jack realizes that he may need to fight the skeletons.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Jack trips on a vase. The sound alerts the skeletons to his presence.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Sam finds no traps so he decides it is safe to continue forward.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Sam touches the ground triggering a pressure plate. This releases a boulder which falls grazing his shoulder dealing damage.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Sam finds no traps so he decides it is safe to continue forward.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Sam touches the ground triggering a pressure plate. This releases a boulder which falls grazing his shoulder dealing damage.
